[Warning] The Data Type Conversion block Data Type Conversion8 is not necessary because the input and output data type are both single.
[Whitelisted] The output of this block is not defined in ADD, and the data type is not single hence the conversion block is needed.

[Warning] The option Integer rounding mode in block Product is set to Nearest instead of Simplest. Rounding methods other than Simplest may lead to abnormal/strange and difficult to debug rounding behavior (see example in documentation and ticket BTCM-668).
[Whitelisted] Nearest is used on purpose to assure accuracy
